# Murzino, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Murzino () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kabansky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 48 as of 2010. There is 1 street.
Geography
Murzino is located 20&nbsp;km northwest of Kabansk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Shigayevo is the nearest rural locality.
